            h2#chapter6 6. Recommendations
           
           p  Another option of SOR from the left side of the screen is Recommendations. Practically this offers the opportunity to receive random recommendations of Books, Films, Events and Educational Institutes based on the user Google account.
            p 
                img(src="images/recommendations.png" alt="sor")
            
            h2#chapter7 7.  Favorites and Report
            p The user can save to Favorites some liked results and also check the report of the presentation in Report option. 
            p 
                img(src="images/favorites.png" alt="sor")
            h2#chapter8 8.  Logout
            p Lastly, to leave the application, use the Log out option from the top right side of the screen. This signs out from user’s account. 
            
            h2#chapter9 9. Conclusion
            p As a conclusion, Social Recommender is a web application that user social networks (Google) and other external resources to recommend the user certain people, events, place, books and films.
            p Feel free to check out SOR!
           
